Traditional healer Credo Mutwa has passed on at the age of 98. A family member confirmed it to daily Sun. Mutwa was well-regarded for his predictions of world events. WATCH: Credo Mutwa's house handover His famous predictions include the destruction of New York’s World Trade Centre in 2001, the 1976 June 16 uprising, HIV, Chris Hani’s assassination, load shedding and the ousting of President Thabo Mbeki. This is a developing story, more details to follow. Meanwhile, tributes continue to pour in on social media for the veteran traditional healer. 